### Hadith 2:285

*Narrated Ibn 'Umar:*

The Prophet used to go to the Mosque of Quba (sometimes) walking and
sometimes riding. Added Nafi (in another narration), "He then would
offer two Rakat (in the Mosque of Quba)."

